briefDescription: The New LEED trust' an NGO working for underprivileged and economically backward people in and around Chennai for the past 20years .where we have a project centre at Thiruvalluvar Nagar, Perungudi,chennai through which we conduct  Skill Development Training Program like tailoring, basket making etc for women,Library, computer training program to educate women and youth to be self sustainable and economically independent, apart from that we organize Family Development programs for women. for details - www.leed.in
